name: Vintage_Wooden_Dinner_Table
reviews: This table seems to be a beautiful table. Rustic and antique...just what I wanted until I saw the deminsions!!! 23 inches wide?????? This is not a dinner table! This is ...what? A utility table? If this table was large enough to seat 4 I would order it in a second!!!!
description:
Handcrafted from reclaimed elm wood, this wonderful table is made in the style of the traditional Chinese dining tables. Very rustic and distinct style, each one is slightly different and beautiful.
